Q-Cells Studies Insurance Under Bankruptcy Scenario, FTD Says

-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 
2011-08-25T11:55:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/q-cells-studies-insurance-under-bankruptcy-scenario-ftd-says.html
Q-Cells SE (QCE)  is studying whether to
offer customers of its solar modules insurance to cover warranty
claims in case of bankruptcy, Financial Times Deutschland
 reported , citing an interview with Chief Executive Officer Nedim Cen.  The policy is aimed at resolving client concerns, the
newspaper said. Q-Cells also hired the investment bank Houlihan
Lokey to look into mid-term financing, the newspaper said. Two
calls and an e-mail to the company’s communications department
seeking comment weren’t returned today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stefan Nicola in Berlin at 
 snicola2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Reed Landberg at 
 landberg@bloomberg.net  